connection_data.text:
Fingrid shall assess the request for a derogation
based on the following criteria:
1) the derogation does not compromise the system security of the power system;
2) the derogation does not restrict the transmission capacity of the power system;
3) the electrical equipment does not cause disturbance to the other parties
connected to the power system;
4) the derogation is technically and commercially justified; and
5) the derogation may be granted in the future in a similar situation impartially and
without discriminating against any future electrical equipment connections

